    <p>Shurget's total liability for any claim arising from these Terms shall not exceed the amount you paid us in the 30 days preceding the claim.</p>
    <p><strong>Items you move are your responsibility.</strong> You should inspect items upon delivery and note any damage on the delivery confirmation. Shurget is not responsible for pre-existing damage. Drivers are not covered by Shurget for property damage — you should resolve any damage claims directly with the driver.</p>

